SupplierContext is a Form
    Layout
        six column distributed
            column1
                Picture.File
                    display as portrait image up to 5 lines
                        missing image is random background
            column2
                SupplierGroup
            column3
                SupplierGroup.Description
                    no label
                    display as text
            column4
                visible when (SupplierExists)
                    Supplier
                        display as text
            column5
                SupplierName
                    label is "Name"
            column6
                visible when (SupplierExists)
                    SupplierStatus
                        label is "Status"
                        display as text
        single column
            SupplierDescription
                use text area of 2 lines
                display as required when (SupplierGroup.RequireSupplierDescription)
